com.yworks.yfiles.graphml

Class PropertyInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.reflect.AccessibleObject
      • com.yworks.yfiles.graphml.PropertyInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnnotatedElement, Member

    public class PropertyInfo
extends AccessibleObject
implements Member
    A PropertyInfo provides information about a property of a java class.

    It consist of a getter and/or setter Method and can be easily created by TypeExtensions.getProperty(Class, String, BindingFlags).
